(SKELETON - NO LOGIC YET)
(Future: quick in-program check that tool intact - position over beam,)
(read laser-broken pin, abort program if tool missing/short)

o<laser_broken_check> sub
    o100 if [#5399 NE 1]
        (abort, LASER: Touch off Z first before broken tool check)
    o100 endif
    (DEBUG, LASER: broken tool check - SKELETON, no logic yet)
o<laser_broken_check> endsub

M2
